text: Princess Iman bint Al Hussein (born April 24, 1983) is the daughter of the late King Hussein of Jordan and Queen Noor. She is the half-sister of the present Jordanian king, Abdullah II. Princess Iman was educated at the Royal Military Academy Sandhurst in England. Category:Jordanian princes and princesses Category:1983 births Category:Living people
title: Princess Iman bint Al Hussein
